data.text:
Player’s Championship Standings

Below you can find an overview of all points you have gathered during the Swiss portion of our 2023 DOS season.

Players in bold are already qualified by winning a DOS event!

Players in italic are qualified based on the standings in the PC 2023 ranking.

Note that these standings are still under review. Please contact us if you think anything is wrong.
